  "npcs": [
    {
      "name": "Courage",
      "x": 8,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "Monster",
      "sprite_index": 2,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Courage",
        "portrait": "Monster",
        "face_index": 2,
        "lines": [
          "I committed a buffer overflow fix right before Evie rang the bell. I still have the cognitive zoomies so I'm going to write some Rust!",
          "It's a full moon, the sky is clear, and I love coding. Awooooooo!"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Ocean",
      "x": 14,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "People4",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Ocean",
        "portrait": "People4",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "I'm not the best programmer and Luna's not the best tester. As a pair we kick butt.",
          "It's almost as if we and the computers and the code all become one in the simulation.",
          "Heh, sorry. I don't know if it's the cybernetics papers or Trek fics that make me like this."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Nyaanager Evie",
      "x": 6,
      "y": 9,
      "sprite": "Nature",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "right",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Nyaanager Evie",
        "portrait": "Nature",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "I love my team and they totally rock. I do my best to protect them but the pressure from Mahogany Row is getting to me.",
          "I can't get promoted without driving my team harder and I know in my toebeans that it would halt their growth."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Glenn Gary",
      "x": 18,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "Actor1",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Glenn Gary",
        "portrait": "Actor1",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "How am I supposed to sell this product when it keeps crashing in front of prospects!?",
          "Inferno talks a big game but really their customers are stuck with us so they put up with it. Our reputation is not great.",
          "The Disco geeks always deliver, eventually. They're never on time and releases are rough. They're always too busy to talk.",
          "I hear the SREs are pretty good but I only know them from incidents, so it's hard for me to tell.",
          "I talked to Mahogany peeps and they say everything is fine. It is in fact, not fine. Except for Marathon, I don't get it."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Shelly the Intern",
      "x": 16,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "Actor3",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Shelly the Intern",
        "portrait": "Actor3",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "These guys aren't paying me enough. They aren't paying me anything!",
          "The Boss brought in a new developer metrics tool to figure out our quality problems...",
          "He berated me for my mean time to review metric. So Leah stamps all my commits now to keep him happy."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Doctor Mcfire",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "DrMcfire",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Doctor McFire",
        "portrait": "DrMcfire",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "On-call is such a rush. One minute you're typing away and the next you're the incident commander.",
          "When I went from the SLO alert to traces I immediately knew I screwed up. Rolling forward was just as easy as rollback so I cut a pull request.",
          "Some people complain but I love incidents. I should write a paper about them, that would be cool."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "The Boss",
      "x": 8,
      "y": 12,
      "sprite": "Monster",
      "sprite_index": 7,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "up",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "The Boss",
        "portrait": "Monster",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "These darn Millenials don't want to work. When I was a lad we wrote COBOL and we hustled and look at me! I turned out fine.",
          "The security bots are on my case about so-called vulnerabilities. I threatened the team with termination if they write bugs, so that's fixed."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Hidaslo Xela",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "People3",
      "sprite_index": 6,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Hidaslo Xela",
        "portrait": "People3",
        "face_index": 6,
        "lines": [
          "I know I'm not supposed to gloat but the error budget alert was the first to fire and we were on it before customers noticed.",
          "Nobody else is doing SLOs yet. I believe SLOs will help the Disco push back on Mahogany Row and keep Inferno honest."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Vee Peapod",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 9,
      "sprite": "People4",
      "sprite_index": 6,
      "step_anime": false,
      "facing": "left",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Vee Peapod",
        "portrait": "People4",
        "face_index": 6,
        "lines": [
          "I heard Cee Eeoh needs a new color wheel in the app so I told Team Disco to get that ready as soon as possible.",
          "They complained about interrupting their sprint but I need to impress the board to get more headcount."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Managear Greg",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 12,
      "sprite": "Greg",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": false,
      "facing": "up",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Managear Greg",
        "portrait": "Greg",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "My director says I always have to have a plan for every problem so we're kinda stuck. I don't know what to do."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Isabella",
      "x": 14,
      "y": 12,
      "sprite": "Isabella",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "up",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Isabella",
        "portrait": "Isabella",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "We're so far behind. They keep giving us more work than we can do. I feel stretched to my limit!"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Polly Math",
      "x": 16,
      "y": 12,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "up",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Polly Math",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "I need to fix this bug then check in the code I started this morning but then BAM! an incident and tests to fix and patch my kernels",
          "Managear says my promotion isn't looking good because I don't close enough tickets. Everything would fall to pieces without me!",
          "Why would you bring up ADHD?"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Devo Pestorius",
      "x": 18,
      "y": 12,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 5,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "up",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Devo Pestorius",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 5,
        "lines": [
          "Our CI/CD is amazing, I should know. So why the heck are we so slow!?"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Alls Johnpaw",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 11,
      "sprite": "Evil",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "left",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Dave",
        "portrait": "Evil",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "GAME OVER MAN!",
          "Haha not really. $#@@*** this though. I gave them the best Kubers and somehow they always have excuses for their outages.",
          "Can you find the root cause for me?",
          "No."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Cody",
      "x": 6,
      "y": 11,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "right",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Cody",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "Stories are never ready for us to work on so I spend all my time chasing requirements."
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
