      "target_scene": "",
      "target_spawn_x": 8,
      "target_spawn_y": 5,
      "trigger": "action",
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "Nyaanager Evie",
          "portrait": "Nature",
          "face_index": 4,
          "text": "Thanks for helping us with this incident Amy. It seems simple technically, but I know in my toebeans there's more to the story."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Amy",
          "portrait": "Amy",
          "face_index": 0,
          "text": "I'll summarize the incident to make sure we're all on the same page."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Amy",
          "portrait": "Amy",
          "face_index": 0,
          "text": "Now, let's talk about contributing factors!"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Isabella",
          "portrait": "Isabella",
          "face_index": 0,
          "text": "I feel terrible about letting the deploy hang around half-failed. It's worked flawlessly for so long I think I just assumed production was fine."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Doctor McFire",
          "portrait": "DrMcfire",
          "face_index": 0,
          "text": "It happens to all of us Isabella. From what we've heard, it sounds like your team is saturated. Accidents are inevitable!"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Doctor McFire",
          "portrait": "DrMcfire",
          "face_index": 0,
          "text": "Can we monitor for broken schemas?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Devo Pestorius",
          "portrait": "People1",
          "face_index": 5,
          "text": "I added failed migration detection to the pipeline before the incident was over. This won't happen again."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Managear Greg",
          "portrait": "Greg",
          "face_index": 0,
          "text": "I realize we've been pushing the team pretty hard. I'm going to push back harder on Mahogany Row when they push for more than we can do."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "The Boss",
          "portrait": "Monster",
          "face_index": 3,
          "text": "You're coddling them. It's your team so whatever. Are we going to talk about how your change broke our product!?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Hidaslo Xela",
          "portrait": "People3",
          "face_index": 6,
          "text": "Tooting my own horn here, but without those error budget alerts we would have been down longer."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Courage",
          "portrait": "Monster",
          "face_index": 2,
          "text": "I haven't done live DDL updates like that in years. It was invvvvvigorating!"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Paws Alljohn",
          "portrait": "Evil",
          "face_index": 3,
          "text": "Team Disco was surprised by something they've never seen before, an unknown unknown."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Paws Alljohn",
          "portrait": "Evil",
          "face_index": 3,
          "text": "When these folks used their expertise to diagnose and manually revert, that was adaptive capacity in action."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Shelly the Intern",
          "portrait": "Actor3",
          "face_index": 3,
          "text": "Wait a minute Paws. Is that the resilience stuff you're always talking about?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Paws Alljohn",
          "portrait": "Evil",
          "face_index": 3,
          "text": "Yep. Exactly. Adaptive capacity in action is resilience."
        }
      ]
    },
